{"tid":1667486,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"全部同我入黎，台灣大學生勇武聲援香港冇人理","createTime":"2019-10-21T13:21:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-21T13:29:08.000Z","uid":47194,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"550f0e742c7606d6e30a465cd5e02e47507c3eef","tid":1667486,"uid":47194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T13:21:11.000Z","msg":"今天要說一個我沒去香港的故事<br />\n<br />\n【香港的悲劇是給你這樣消費的嗎？】<br />\n在香港長達數個月、充滿悲傷的抗爭中，你是否有想過：居然有人會拿香港的悲劇來消費，假裝自己參與了香港激烈的抗爭、欺騙大眾？<br />\n而這樣的人，居然用自己虛構的經歷去高中演講，與學生們分享那些 #憑空杜撰的抗爭事蹟？？？<br />\n#香港不是拿來給你消費的<br />\n#想知道真相請看下去<br />\n<br />\n消費香港懶人包<br />\n1.拿記者的的照片與文章，聲稱是自己所見<br />\n2.說自己與黑警衝突重傷，其實根本沒受傷<br />\n3.說有去香港，卻被目擊人在台灣<br />\n4.藉由勇武形象獲取系上教授、同學支持<br />\n5.即將打著系上名號去高中演講騙人"},{"pid":"e9b2e91c0bfb9cac6dfa14e9ee2bfa5636f1aafe","tid":1667486,"uid":47194,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T13:21:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GeHBaJw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGeHBaJw.jpg&h=09519fda&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"96ffc9447af964706ccbb781f5bab1f357d66c8a","tid":1667486,"uid":47194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T13:22:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wL9WVaq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwL9WVaq.jpg&h=bac6b3d9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8a0005b6b345db5f213e4c21f93db0accb7ce25a","tid":1667486,"uid":47194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T13:22:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VAGycXg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVAGycXg.jpg&h=028cbb6b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8bcb9c504e95f85ec636c8cac11f65f64eb75c5a","tid":1667486,"uid":47194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T13:23:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Or3XECB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOr3XECB.jpg&h=cdc5d